<lb n="0188a13" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0188a14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0188a15" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 861</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0188a16" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0188002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】延享元年刊大正大學藏本，【甲】平安時代寫本高山寺藏豐山版</note>毘盧遮那五字真言修習儀軌</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0188a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0188a18" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">三藏<note n="0188003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不空金剛＝金剛不空智奉【甲】</note><app n="0188003"><lem wit="【大】">不空金剛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">金剛不空智奉</rdg></app>　<note n="0188004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（奉）&M062485;＋詔【原】</note><sic n="0188004" resp="【原】" corr="奉詔">詔</sic>譯</byline>
<lb n="0188a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188a1901">夫修習成就毘盧遮那佛法。先應於閑淨處
<lb n="0188a20" ed="T"/>以瞿摩夷塗地。香水散灑燒種種名香。散種
<lb n="0188a21" ed="T"/>種時花。當於寂靜<note n="0188005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辦＝辭&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0188005" resp="【原】" corr="辭">辦</sic>喧鬧。清淨澡浴著新
<lb n="0188a22" ed="T"/>淨衣結跏趺坐。或<note n="0188006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">依＋（求四種法座所謂息災增益敬　降伏）【甲】</note><app n="0188006"><lem wit="【大】">依</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">依求四種法座所謂息災增益敬　降伏</rdg></app>類而坐。息災吉祥<note n="0188007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">坐＝座【甲】＊</note><app n="0188007"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188a23" ed="T"/>面向北。增益蓮花<app source="0188007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>面向東。敬愛金剛<app source="0188007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188a24" ed="T"/>面向西。降伏蹲踞<app source="0188007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">座</rdg></app>以&CB00560;押&CB00560;面向南。隨所
<lb n="0188a25" ed="T"/>愛樂依方而坐。即以香泥塗手。於頂上合掌
<lb n="0188a26" ed="T"/>禮敬一切諸佛。然於下方從風輪起想<note n="0188008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】＊</note><app n="0188008"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>字。
<lb n="0188a27" ed="T"/>以二點嚴飾。如<note n="0188009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">金＋（剛）【甲】</note><app n="0188009"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">金剛</rdg></app>形放熾盛光。威猛赫<app><lem wit="【CBETA】">奕</lem><rdg wit="【大】">弈</rdg></app>金
<lb n="0188a28" ed="T"/>剛火焰壞破大地。上衝流出。則想此金剛火
<lb n="0188a29" ed="T"/>焰焚燒自身。乃至灰<note n="0188010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謝＝&CB13789;【甲】</note><app n="0188010"><lem wit="【大】">謝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB13789;</rdg></app>隨四種法色。想灰成
<pb n="0188b" id="T18.0861.0188b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0188b01" ed="T"/>曼拏羅。即於曼荼羅中想一蓮花。於蓮花中
<lb n="0188b02" ed="T"/>想<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>字。轉成金剛形。想己身為金剛所成。</p>
<lb n="0188b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b0301">即結三昧耶印　二手作三普吒掌。&CB00594;二大
<lb n="0188b04" ed="T"/>指加持於五處。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b0501" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃阿三迷怛哩<note n="0188011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><app n="0188011"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>三迷三
<lb n="0188b06" ed="T"/>摩曳莎縛<note place="inline">二合</note>訶<note n="0188012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【甲】</note><note n="0188012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔引〕－【甲】<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0188012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b0701">次結法界印　二手作拳。二大指在掌中&CB00594;。
<lb n="0188b08" ed="T"/>二頭指。想<note n="0188013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【甲】</note><app n="0188013"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羅</rdg></app>字於頂上。思惟真實義。一切
<lb n="0188b09" ed="T"/>法塵不可得。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b1001" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃達<note n="0188014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝磨【甲】</note><app n="0188014"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">磨</rdg></app>馱<note n="0188015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">都＝&CB00418;【甲】</note><app n="0188015"><lem wit="【大】">都</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00418;</rdg></app>娑&CB00085;婆&CB00085;
<lb n="0188b11" ed="T"/>俱<note n="0188016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吽＝唅【甲】</note><note n="0188016" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB00292;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">吽</rdg></app>＝唅【甲】</note><app n="0188016"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00292;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唅</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b1201">次結次輪印　二手反相叉。<note n="0188017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝左【甲】</note><app n="0188017"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">左</rdg></app>大指在右手
<lb n="0188b13" ed="T"/>掌中相著。觀自身為金剛薩埵。合以加持。真
<lb n="0188b14" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b1501" type="dharani">那謨三曼多<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日<anchor id="fxT18p0188b03"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>喃<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日<anchor id="fxT18p0188b05"/>囉<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT18p0188b06"/>引</note>
<lb n="0188b16" ed="T"/>怛摩俱唅</p>
<lb n="0188b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b1701">次結甲冑印　二手三普吒掌。二頭指屈<note n="0188018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拄＝跓【甲】</note><app n="0188018"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">跓</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188b18" ed="T"/>中指背上節。二大指並&CB00594;合在掌印五處。真
<lb n="0188b19" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b2001" type="dharani">那謨三曼多&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>喃<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日羅迦<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>遮
<lb n="0188b21" ed="T"/>吽</p>
<lb n="0188b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b2201">則於自身前想大蓮華王。於蓮華中想金色
<lb n="0188b23" ed="T"/>佉字。其佉字轉成婆伽梵大勤勇尊。住之三
<lb n="0188b24" ed="T"/>摩地結劍印。即結如來鉤印奉請本尊。<note n="0188019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＋（手）【甲】</note><app n="0188019"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二手</rdg></app>內
<lb n="0188b25" ed="T"/>相叉作拳。&CB00594;右頭指如鉤向身招之。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188b26" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b2601" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃<note n="0188020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">噁＝惡【甲】</note><app n="0188020"><lem wit="【大】">噁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">惡</rdg></app>娑<note n="0188021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔囉〕－【甲】</note><app n="0188021"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00085;怛<anchor id="fxT18p0188b09"/>囉&CB00425;羅
<lb n="0188b27" ed="T"/>底訶多怛多<note n="0188022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00617;＋（多）【甲】，（黨）&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0188022"><lem wit="【大】"><sic resp="【原】" corr="＆CB00617；黨">&CB00617;</sic></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00617;多</rdg></app>俱舍&CB00155;地者哩耶&CB00425;哩布<anchor id="fxT18p0188b10"/>囉
<lb n="0188b28" ed="T"/>迦娑<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app source="0188012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188b29" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188b2901">聖眾來已。即奉閼伽　二手<note n="0188023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捧＋（器）【甲】</note><app n="0188023"><lem wit="【大】">捧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">捧器</rdg></app>當額想浴聖
<pb n="0188c" id="T18.0861.0188c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0188c01" ed="T"/>眾真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c0201" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃哦哦那三摩三摩娑<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0188c03" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app source="0188012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c0401">次獻敷座印　二手虛心合掌。散舒<note n="0188024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">屈＋（頭中名）&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0188024" resp="【原】" corr="屈頭中名">屈</sic>六指
<lb n="0188c05" ed="T"/>如蓮花形。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c0601" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<note n="0188025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">喃＝南【甲】＊</note><app n="0188025"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>噁</p>
<lb n="0188c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c0701">次結聖不動尊印　二手各作拳。各&CB00594;頭中
<lb n="0188c08" ed="T"/>指。各以二大指押無名指小指。左手為鞘。右
<lb n="0188c09" ed="T"/>手為刀。以刀左旋轉辟除諸魔障。右旋轉及
<lb n="0188c10" ed="T"/>上下成方隅界。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c1101" type="dharani">那謨三曼多<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>日羅<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00718;戰拏摩訶嚧灑拏
<lb n="0188c12" ed="T"/>薩叵吒耶吽怛<note n="0188026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＋（二合）&M062485;夾註【原】</note><sic n="0188026" resp="【原】" corr="囉(二合)">囉</sic>吒<note n="0188027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00292;＝吽【甲】</note><app n="0188027"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00292;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">吽</rdg></app>&CB00805;</p>
<lb n="0188c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c1301">復以刀印觸香花<note n="0188028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">求＝水【甲】，等&M062485;【原】</note><note n="0188028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">求＝水【甲】，＝等&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0188028"><lem wit="【大】"><sic resp="【原】" corr="等">求</sic></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">水</rdg></app>無垢令淨。以成加護置
<lb n="0188c14" ed="T"/>於鞘中。</p>
<lb n="0188c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c1501">次結毘盧遮那五字劍印　二手合掌屈二頭
<lb n="0188c16" ed="T"/>指相著。如劍形。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c1701" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃阿尾<anchor id="fxT18p0188c04"/>囉吽欠</p>
<lb n="0188c18" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c1801">次結塗香印　右手掌向外。以左手。<note n="0188029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">握＝掘【甲】</note><app n="0188029"><lem wit="【大】">握</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">掘</rdg></app>右手
<lb n="0188c19" ed="T"/>腕如環。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c2001" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<app source="0188025" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>尾&CB02122;&CB00499;<note n="0188030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">巘＝獻【甲】</note><app n="0188030"><lem wit="【大】">巘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">獻</rdg></app>塗納婆吠娑
<lb n="0188c21" ed="T"/><app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app source="0188012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c2201">次結花印　二手內相叉。仰掌頭指<note n="0188031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（相）＋著【甲】</note><app n="0188031"><lem wit="【大】">著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">相著</rdg></app>。二大
<lb n="0188c23" ed="T"/>指安頭指下節。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0188c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c2401" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<app source="0188025" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>摩訶每怛哩耶<note place="inline">二合</note>毘愈
<lb n="0188c25" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>娜&CB00617;底娑<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app source="0188012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0188c26" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c2601">次結燒香印　二手中指無名指小指背合
<lb n="0188c27" ed="T"/>&CB00594;。頭指直&CB00594;傾相合。大指在頭指下節。真言
<lb n="0188c28" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0188c29" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0188c2901" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<app source="0188025" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>達摩&CB00499;<note n="0188032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00418;&CB00085;娜＝&CB03377;拏【甲】</note><app n="0188032"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00418;&CB00085;娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB03377;拏</rdg></app>&CB00617;帝
<pb n="0189a" id="T18.0861.0189a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0189a01" ed="T"/><note n="0189001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">莎＝婆【甲】</note><app n="0189001"><lem wit="【大】">莎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">婆</rdg></app><app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app source="0188012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189a0201">次結飲食<note n="0189002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔真言〕－【甲】</note><app n="0189002"><lem wit="【大】">真言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>印　當合定惠。掌五輪互相
<lb n="0189a03" ed="T"/>叉。是則持眾物。普通供養印。</p>
<lb n="0189a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189a0401" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱喃阿<anchor id="fxT18p0189a03"/>囉<anchor id="fxT18p0189a04"/>囉迦<anchor id="fxT18p0189a05"/>囉<anchor id="fxT18p0189a06"/>囉<note n="0189003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">末＝未【甲】＊</note><app n="0189003"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">未</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a05" ed="T"/>&CB00444;捺那<note n="0189004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迷＋（摩&CB00444;上聲娜泥摩訶麼理）&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0189004" resp="【原】" corr="迷摩＆CB00444；上聲娜泥摩訶麼理">迷</sic>娑<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app source="0188012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189a06" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189a0601">次結<note n="0189005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">燈＋（明）【甲】</note><app n="0189005"><lem wit="【大】">燈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">燈明</rdg></app>印。右手作拳。中指直&CB00594;。頭指屈<note n="0189006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大捻＝捻大【甲】</note><app n="0189006"><lem wit="【大】">大
<lb n="0189a07" ed="T"/>捻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">捻大</rdg></app>。指博附中指。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189a0801" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<app source="0188025" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>多他&CB00617;多哩紙薩叵<anchor id="fxT18p0189a10"/>囉
<lb n="0189a09" ed="T"/>拏<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>婆娑那哦哦那烏馱哩耶娑<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶
<lb n="0189a10" ed="T"/><app source="0188012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189a1101">所獻塗香花鬘燒香飲食燈明。隨四種法色。
<lb n="0189a12" ed="T"/>而以供養。由五種供養印。成於聖眾集會普
<lb n="0189a13" ed="T"/>遍香花等雲海供養。</p>
<lb n="0189a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189a1401">次結圓滿印。二手虛心合掌安於頂上。真
<lb n="0189a15" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189a1601" type="dharani">那謨三曼多沒馱<app source="0188025" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">喃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南</rdg></app>噁尾娑摩曳娑叵<anchor id="fxT18p0189a15"/>囉呬
<lb n="0189a17" ed="T"/>&CB00805;哦哦那劍達摩馱怛<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>迦舍三摩多耶娑
<lb n="0189a18" ed="T"/><app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>怛他<note n="0189007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00617;＋（多）【甲】</note><app n="0189007"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00617;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00617;多</rdg></app><note n="0189008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跛＝跋&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0189008" resp="【原】" corr="跋">跛</sic>哩<note n="0189009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">剎＝殺【甲】</note><app n="0189009"><lem wit="【大】">剎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">殺</rdg></app>曼荼羅摩摩本惹<app source="0189003" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">未</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a19" ed="T"/>禮拏怛他&CB00617;多地瑟&CB00109;那<app source="0189003" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">未</rdg></app>禮那遮迷娑<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a20" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app source="0188012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189a2101">由此真言印香花等雲海供養。如實<note n="0189010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無＋（異）【甲】</note><app n="0189010"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">無異</rdg></app>即用
<lb n="0189a22" ed="T"/>五字。從下體布至頂。地水火風空。即想自身
<lb n="0189a23" ed="T"/>如金色毘盧遮那佛。<note n="0189011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍＋（身）&M062485;【原】，（放）&M062485;【原】</note>遍光明頭冠瓔珞身著
<lb n="0189a24" ed="T"/>紗縠衣。即結劍印安於當心住三摩地。二手
<lb n="0189a25" ed="T"/>持珠。合於掌中誦真言七遍。加持安<note n="0189012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔於〕－【甲】</note><app n="0189012"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>頂
<lb n="0189a26" ed="T"/>上。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189a27" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189a2701" type="dharani">唵吠盧者那摩羅娑<app source="0188008" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<app source="0188012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189a2801">然後二手當心。持珠念誦本尊<note n="0189013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（真）＋言【甲】</note><app n="0189013"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">真言</rdg></app>。遍數畢
<lb n="0189a29" ed="T"/><note n="0189014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝竟【甲】</note><app n="0189014"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">竟</rdg></app>。安珠於掌中。頂上合掌迴向發願。以此
<pb n="0189b" id="T18.0861.0189b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0189b01" ed="T"/>功德當願眾生速證毘盧遮那佛。放念珠已。
<lb n="0189b02" ed="T"/>然後結定印。端身正坐於<note n="0189015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頂＋（上）【甲】</note><app n="0189015"><lem wit="【大】">頂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">頂上</rdg></app>中想白色闇字。
<lb n="0189b03" ed="T"/>於二目瞳人上想覽字。即微屈頭注心於胸
<lb n="0189b04" ed="T"/>臆閒想圓<note n="0189016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">滿＝明【甲】</note><app n="0189016"><lem wit="【大】">滿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">明</rdg></app>月輪。於月輪上布列五字。想阿
<lb n="0189b05" ed="T"/>字在中央如黃金色。餘四字右旋而安。</p>
<lb n="0189b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189b0601">五字真實義者。</p>
<lb n="0189b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189b0701">阿字一切法本不生故　尾字思義一切法言
<lb n="0189b08" ed="T"/>說不可得故　<anchor id="fxT18p0189b01"/>囉字一切法離塵故　訶字一
<lb n="0189b09" ed="T"/>切法因不可得故　佉字一<note n="0189017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">切＋（法）【甲】</note><app n="0189017"><lem wit="【大】">切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">切法</rdg></app>如虛空<note n="0189018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔不可得〕－【甲】</note><app n="0189018"><lem wit="【大】">不可
<lb n="0189b10" ed="T"/>得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>故。名為心念誦。</p>
<lb n="0189b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189b1101">即結劍印誦七遍頂上散。復結五供養印。獻
<lb n="0189b12" ed="T"/>閼伽讚歎。結不<note n="0189019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">動＋（尊）【甲】</note><app n="0189019"><lem wit="【大】">動</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">動尊</rdg></app>劍印。左旋解界。結三<note n="0189020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">昧＋（耶）【甲】</note><app n="0189020"><lem wit="【大】">昧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">昧耶</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189b13" ed="T"/>印安於頂上誦三遍。想奉送聖眾。禮佛而起
<lb n="0189b14" ed="T"/>隨意經行。讀誦大乘方廣經典。以福迴施一
<lb n="0189b15" ed="T"/>切眾生願速圓滿心所求。世閒出世閒悉地
<lb n="0189b16" ed="T"/>成就也。</p>
<lb n="0189b17" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>毘盧遮那念誦<note n="0189021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一卷＝經【甲】</note><app n="0189021"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">經</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
<lb n="0189b18" ed="T"/><note n="0189022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔延享…焉〕五十五字－【甲】</note><app word-count="55" n="0189022"><lem wit="【大】"><div1 type="W"><p id="pT18p0189b1801">延享改元夏用亡弟僧尊隆遺財而刻是軌
<lb n="0189b19" ed="T"/>以遂其宿志伏祈法乳永潤法界云　藤原
<lb n="0189b20" ed="T"/>常香謹誌</p>
<lb n="0189b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0189b2101">時延享元甲子秋八月念三豐山無等&CB00677;挍
<lb n="0189b22" ed="T"/>焉</p></div1></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>
</body></text></TEI.2>